@startuml
title Authentication Flow

actor Alice
participant "Auth Server" as Bob
database "User DB" as DB

Alice -> Bob: Login request (username, password)
activate Bob
Bob -> DB: SELECT user WHERE name=?
DB --> Bob: user record
Bob -> Bob: verify password hash
Bob --> Alice: JWT token
deactivate Bob

Alice -> Bob: GET /profile (JWT)
activate Bob
Bob --> Alice: profile data
deactivate Bob
@enduml
